intake, at the same time, you may have some cardio or weight-training but prefer the latter one because it effectively maintain your muscle mass when you are in energy deficit"},{"pid":"928e6c2acb19167659bc8ccc94b645c27b35fa34","tid":1590902,"uid":212943,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:00:45.000Z","msg":"絲打你反而應該做多d weight training rather than 日日 cardio<br />\n<br />\n我四個月前差唔多165 磅，高176 cm, 腰圍成36.5。到現加147磅，腰32吋度，有埋四舊腹肌。<br />\n<br />\n唔係話做 Cardio 唔好, 之不過唔會練到身材同埋會 skinny fat, 同埋好快反彈，反而一個禮拜做3-4 日 weight training 同飲食個 part 要睇緊d, 唔食甜品同減小電粉質，食多d 高蛋白質既野。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1821148/%E7%B7%B4%E5%87%BA%E5%AE%8C%E7%BE%8E%E7%B7%9A%E6%A2%9D%E5%BF%85%E9%A3%9F%E3%80%8010%E7%A8%AE%E9%AB%98%E8%9B%8B%E7%99%BD%E8%B3%AA%E9%A3%9F%E7%89%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1821148%2F%25E7%25B7%25B4%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25AE%258C%25E7%25BE%258E%25E7%25B7%259A%25E6%25A2%259D%25E5%25BF%2585%25E9%25A3%259F%25E3%2580%258010%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E9%25AB%2598%25E8%259B%258B%25E7%2599%25BD%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E9%25A3%259F%25E7%2589%25A9&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obh3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=aed3a788\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1821148/%E7%B7%B4%E5%87%BA%E5%AE%8C%E7%BE%8E%E7%B7%9A%E6%A2%9D%E5%BF%85%E9%A3%9F%E3%80%8010%E7%A8%AE%E9%AB%98%E8%9B%8B%E7%99%BD%E8%B3%AA%E9%A3%9F%E7%89%A9</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我的餐單:<br />\n<br />\n一日一杯牛奶(高蓋低脂), 三種唔同 color 的水果 (通常係香蕉橙同蘋果)<br />\n<br />\n小食(五粒杏仁，唔好買油炎焗個d, 買藍寶石)<br />\n<br />\n早上: 水浸吞拿魚加兩塊麵包，兩隻雞蛋，一個牛油果(你係絲打就食半個牛油果好 la)<br />\n<br />\n午餐: 小飯(大約半碗飯)，小汁，多菜多肉<br />\n<br />\n晚餐: (大約小半碗飯)，多菜多肉<br />\n<br />\n大約係咁，如果有問題你 TG 我la<br />\n<br />\nTG: wing_donald"},{"pid":"6c0f9f0278e58f88f811b01248634e68e7b698cf","tid":1590902,"uid":327005,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a10379876702f0a19926df22133a867e6b647ea0","tid":1590902,"uid":63508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"201